{
  "stem": "18581.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I used to hear a motor, because no-- none of the local people had a motor car.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So if it was a motor car it must have been either police or army.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So whenever I heard the-- and we were quite removed from the road.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I could easily sneak out into the woods, because it was a wooded area.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I had a place prepared two, three miles away.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When everything quietened down, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] they left, I used to come back.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the farmer's wife once asked me, why did you go away?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I mean, are you OK?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I said, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You see, the Germans might draft me into the-- into work or into the Lithuanian battalions.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I don't want to go to the front.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't trust the Germans more than I trust the Russians.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm a Lithuanian nationalist.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the Russians didn't-- didn't honor our freedom, neither did the Germans.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They did not keep their word that they're going to restore independent Lithuania.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Lithuania became another district of the eastern provinces.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We knew more or less the progress of the war, sometimes from the priest and sometimes from other people that were connected with the Armia Krajowa.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Armia Krajowa was a Polish underground.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were two, Armia Krajowa and Armia Ludowa.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The Armia Krajowa was anti-Semitic and often killed Jews.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In yesterday's there was an article that you should-- I mean, one should read about what they did after the war.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, praying, singing quietly [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Israeli songs, Hebrew songs that I knew, and thinking and planning my life, what I will do in Palestine after Hitler is defeated and I run away from the Russians.",
      "word_count": 38
    }
  ],
